channel.title: Project Insanity
channel.description:
Hey guys, That moderated thing over to the left is nothing bad really. I had a arguement with someone and i admit i got abit roudy.
Anyways, People who are new to coding and even people who are veteran to coding could find this useful. I have had this for a long long time and all the other links for it have died.
Hope u guys like it, There is no anti leech as there isnt much to leech really, This is a good starter base to use for your first 317 project insanity.
How to make it webclient ready: Click [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=449295.0]here[/url]. How to make a webclient: Click [url=https://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=509727.0]here[/url].
Add me on skype for any help, Just put my email in the search bar. JoeeBentonn3@gmail.com. Dont email me btw, I wont reply to them because i hardly check my mail inbox.
Download links:
The screenshots: Click [url=https://dl.dropbox.com/s/gt8fkbzk8rfkdnq/Images.zip]here[/url]. The source files: Click [url=https://dl.dropbox.com/s/u24akydpi59ek75/Client.zip]here[/url] The client files: Click [url=https://dl.dropbox.com/s/99hljyzect01d4z/Server.zip]here[/url].
You will need winRAR of course. Click [url=http://www.rarlab.com]here[/url] if you havent already got it.
Okay now for some media:
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/q0gns7mo2qpzw8m/Media.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/mm5u978z97f2rx6/Login.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/7e4tanthmij5p2t/LoginBox.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/q3wtikmgpk1idrt/Shops.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/rw1sc1fi9bjz1y4/Original.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/vy02idoapocwysj/Levels.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/cfd3pp59vv2xbzh/Comment.png[/img]
[img]https://dl.dropbox.com/s/ksn33qseuqupk35/Cya%20Guys.png[/img]
Thanks for looking, I hope this helped some people out there. Please dont flame just because you dont like it. At least im trying to give something back to you guys, Mainly them newcomers and beginners.
Credits: I Am Sanity - He made Project Insainty. :cool: Joe_Benton - Grave digging and fixing some bugs. :cool:
